text: Nice place for a casual meal. Enjoyed the mushroom melt, coffee and cold drink (kyoto grape rose) were pretty good but the chocolate banana cake was VERY dry.
This 3 stars are given only for the drinks that we bought to go, coffee is average and the only "takeaway" size is large. Might come back to try their food one day.
Pit stop for a hot tea made cold. Lemongrass detox $4.90. It's refreshing. Pretty n clean cafe. Like d ambience until it's full house. Staff is friendly n attentive.

Great place to catch up with colleagues over coffee and have business meeting discussion.

However, there's not many seatings available for long discussions.

Coffee was alright. Food was not up to expectations as it wasn't as hot as I expected.

Ordered an oat latte and baked vegetables. Food quality can be improved.

Not that the food was terrible, but the coffee wasnâ€™t good.
Definitely not worth the price..
